        "title": "Letter to the Editor Asymptomatic and symptomatic respiratory virus infection detected in naso-pharyngeal swabs from solid organ transplant recipients early after transplantation Keywords: Respiratory virus infection Solid organ transplant patients Immunosuppression",
        "authors": []
    },
